msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/date"
msgid "June 6th, 1944 · Normandy, France"
msgstr "6 de junio de 1944. Normandía, Francia"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/ger_reinf"
msgid "Get ready for the arrival of German reinforcements!"
msgstr "¡Prepárate para la llegada de refuerzos alemanes!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/name"
msgid "The Pathfinders"
msgstr "Los Exploradores"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/name_big"
msgid "The Pathfinders"
msgstr "Los Exploradores"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/"
"fra_civilian/01"
msgid "Come on. We're at war, after all. At least you're still alive!"
msgstr "¡Esto es una guerra! Al menos sigues vivo..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/"
"fra_civilian/02"
msgid ""
"Hey, my American friends! Sorry for the harsh welcome. Life here has become "
"tough for all of us under German occupation, but most of us are glad you are "
"finally here. However, I fear my friend intends to inform the Germans of "
"your position."
msgstr ""
"Hola, amigos estadounidenses. Disculpen la intensa bienvenida. La vida aquí "
"se ha vuelto un poco difícil para todos bajo la ocupación de los alemanes, "
"pero la mayoría nos alegramos de que por fin estéis aquí. Sin embargo, me "
"temo que mi amigo tiene la intención de informar a los alemanes de vuestra "
"posición."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/"
"fra_civilian/03"
msgid "Hey, hey! Americans!"
msgstr "¡Saludos! ¡Americanos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/"
"fra_civilian/04"
msgid ""
"Let us help you! We can't offer anything right now, but know the Germans "
"have left a supply trailer hidden somewhere in the orchards behind us. You "
"may want to check it out. Good luck!"
msgstr ""
"¡Déjenos ayudarle! No podemos ofreceros nada ahora mismo, pero sabemos que "
"los alemanes han dejado un remolque de suministros escondido en algún lugar "
"de los huertos detrás de nosotros. Creo que puede ser interesante ¡Suerte!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/fra_farmer/01"
msgid ""
"God damn it! These self-proclaimed liberators may be worse than the Germans; "
"that horse was all I had left!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita sea! Estos liberadores pueden ser peores que los alemanes ¡ese "
"caballo era todo lo que me quedaba!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/fra_farmer/02"
msgid ""
"I might as well be dead now! You, you godforsaken Americans, had to start a "
"fight here of all places. Now, my only breadwinner is dead! Get lost! You'll "
"pay for this!"
msgstr ""
"¡Soy hombre muerto! Vosotros, malditos americanos, teníais que empezar a "
"dispararos aquí ¿Qué hago ahora sin lo único que me daba de comer? ¡Largo! "
"¡Pagaréis por esto!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/"
"ger_officer/01"
msgid "ALARM!!"
msgstr "¡¡ALARMA!!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/01"
msgid "Thunder!"
msgstr "¡Trueno!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/02"
msgid "Get your ass over here before Jerry sees you!"
msgstr "¡Ven aquí antes de que te vean los boches!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/03"
msgid ""
"Enemy patrol approaching from down the road. Wait until they get close, and "
"let’em have it!"
msgstr ""
"Patrulla enemiga acercándose por el camino. Espera a que se acerquen y "
"dispárales con todo."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/04"
msgid ""
"Alright, I think I know which road this is. On me, troopers, let's take a "
"look at the map!"
msgstr ""
"Muy bien, creo que sé qué camino es este ¡Conmigo, soldados, echemos un "
"vistazo al mapa!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/05"
msgid ""
"Soldiers, let's move East and group up with any paratroopers we find. "
"Remember the code words!"
msgstr ""
"Soldados, movámonos al este y agrupémonos con los paracaidistas que "
"encontremos ¡Recordad las palabras clave!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/06"
msgid ""
"Alright, men, rally on me! Let's move out and see if we can find anyone else!"
msgstr ""
"¡Muy bien, muchachos, reúnanse conmigo! ¡Movámonos y veamos si podemos "
"encontrar a alguien más!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/07"
msgid "Soldiers, you're with me now. Let's go!"
msgstr "Soldados, están conmigo ahora. ¡Adelante!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/08"
msgid "Flash!"
msgstr "¡Rayo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/09"
msgid "Germans approaching from the north!"
msgstr "¡Alemanes acercándose desde el norte!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/10"
msgid ""
"Listen up! We've gathered as many men as we can. Let's have a look at the "
"situation and go over our objectives!"
msgstr ""
"¡Escuchad! Hemos reunido tantos hombres como hemos podido. Analicemos la "
"situación y repasemos los objetivos"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/11"
msgid "More Germans are approaching from the south!"
msgstr "¡Más alemanes se acercan desde el sur!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/12"
msgid ""
"That must be a German officer driving away! Stop him before he can escape "
"and gather reinforcements!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ese que se aleja debe ser un oficial alemán! ¡Deténganlo antes de que pueda "
"escapar y reúnan refuerzos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/13"
msgid ""
"Damn it! That Kraut officer managed to get away! Hopefully, he doesn't come "
"back with some friends!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita sea! ¡Ese oficial logró escapar! ¡Esperemos que no vuelva con ayuda!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/14"
msgid "Good! That Kraut officer won't be going anywhere. Serves him right!"
msgstr "¡Bien! Ese oficial alemán no irá a ninguna parte ¡Se lo merece!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/15"
msgid ""
"Listen up! We have to set up those beacons ASAP. It could sink the whole "
"operation if they're not ready in time!"
msgstr ""
"¡Escuchad! Tenemos que colocar esas balizas lo antes posible ¡Podría echar a "
"perder toda la operación si no están listas a tiempo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/16"
msgid "Let's get close to the coordinates and install the beacons."
msgstr "Acerquémonos a las coordenadas y coloquemos las balizas."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/17"
msgid "Well, you're alright now. Grab your gear and form up on me!"
msgstr "Bueno, ya estás bien. ¡Recordad el equipo y formad conmigo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/18"
msgid ""
"Excellent work men! Hopefully, the rest of the guys will arrive more "
"organized than we did."
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo, muchachos! Esperemos que el resto de los chicos lleguen "
"más organizados que nosotros."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/19"
msgid "Way to go, troopers! Those Flak guns won't be bothering anyone else."
msgstr "¡Así se hace, soldados! Esas Flak no dispararán a nadie más."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/20"
msgid ""
"German vehicles on the move! That Kraut officer came back with his friends! "
"Wipe them all out!"
msgstr ""
"¡Vehículos alemanes en movimiento! ¡Ese oficial alemán volvió con amigos! "
"¡Acabad con todos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/21"
msgid ""
"A good start to the invasion, boys! But we've still got a long day ahead of "
"us. Let's hope our luck holds..."
msgstr ""
"¡Un buen comienzo para la invasión, chicos! Pero todavía tenemos un largo "
"día por delante. Esperemos que nuestra suerte se mantenga..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/22"
msgid ""
"Shit! A large German force is approaching! Did that Frenchman collaborate "
"with the Germans?"
msgstr ""
"¡Mierda! ¡Se acerca una gran fuerza alemana! ¿Ese francés estaba de parte de "
"los alemanes?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/23"
msgid ""
"The main roads will likely have traffic on them. Let's avoid them and any "
"more German patrols."
msgstr ""
"Las carreteras principales probablemente tendrán tráfico. Evitémoslas y "
"también a las patrullas alemanas."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/24"
msgid ""
"Good morning, Lieutenant! Welcome to Normandy! I hope your jump was better "
"than ours!"
msgstr ""
"¡Buenos días, Teniente! ¡Bienvenido a Normandía! ¡Espero que su salto haya "
"sido mejor que el nuestro!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/25"
msgid ""
"No, Lieutenant. You're the first we've seen. We've been too busy slugging it "
"out with the Krauts. Haven't had a moment to catch our breath."
msgstr ""
"No, Teniente. Es el primero que vemos. Hemos estado muy ocupados luchando "
"contra los alemanes. No hemos tenido ni un momento para recuperar el aliento."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/26"
msgid "Good Luck Lieutenant! What's that guy's problem?"
msgstr "¡Buena suerte Teniente! ¿Cuál es el problema de ese tipo?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/officer/27"
msgid "I see... Remind me not to get in his way."
msgstr "Ya veo... Recuérdame que no me interponga en su camino."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier/01"
msgid "Flash!"
msgstr "¡Rayo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier/02"
msgid "Boy, am I glad to see you, Sir!"
msgstr "¡Cómo me alegro de verle, señor!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier/03"
msgid "Whoa! Jerry didn't know what hit him!"
msgstr "¡Guau! ¡Los boches no sabrán qué les golpeó!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier/04"
msgid "Flash!"
msgstr "¡Rayo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier/05"
msgid "Look, Sir! A German staff car is trying to get away!"
msgstr "¡Mire, señor! ¡Un coche de oficiales alemán está intentando escapar!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier/06"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier/07"
msgid "Enemy flak gun is no more!"
msgstr "¡El cañón antiaéreo enemigo ya no será problema!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier/08"
msgid "Flak position silenced!"
msgstr "¡Posición antiaérea eliminada!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier/09"
msgid "Enemy column destroyed, Sir!"
msgstr "¡Columna enemiga destruida, señor!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier2/01"
msgid "Thunder!"
msgstr "¡Trueno!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier2/02"
msgid "Sir! Yes, Sir!"
msgstr "¡Señor! ¡Sí, señor!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier2/03"
msgid "Beacon deployed, Sir!"
msgstr "¡Baliza desplegada, señor!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier3/01"
msgid "Thunder!"
msgstr "¡Trueno!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier3/02"
msgid "Thank god you're here, Sir! We're a little lost."
msgstr "¡Gracias a Dios que está aquí, señor! Estamos un poco perdidos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier4/01"
msgid "Thunder!"
msgstr "¡Trueno!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/soldier4/02"
msgid "Yes Sir! On you, Sir!"
msgstr "¡Sí, señor! ¡Con usted, señor!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/"
"soldier_prisoner/01"
msgid ""
"Sir! Thanks for saving us! We landed right on top of their positions. We "
"didn't stand a chance."
msgstr ""
"¡Señor! ¡Gracias por salvarnos! Aterrizamos justo encima de sus posiciones. "
"No pudimos hacer nada."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/"
"soldier_prisoner/02"
msgid "Yes Sir! Our weapons are here on the table."
msgstr "¡Sí, señor! Nuestras armas están aquí sobre la mesa."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/winters/01"
msgid ""
"Lieutenant Winters, Easy Company, 2nd Battalion. Have you come across anyone "
"else from our Company?"
msgstr ""
"Teniente Winters, Compañía Easy, 2º Batallón ¿Se ha encontrado con alguien "
"más de nuestra compañía?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/winters/02"
msgid "Well, we have our objective to secure and little time to do it."
msgstr "Bueno, tenemos un objetivo que asegurar y poco tiempo para hacerlo."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/winters/03"
msgid ""
"That's \"Wild Bill\". He just found out his brother bought it in Italy, and "
"now he’s got it in for the Krauts."
msgstr ""
"Ese es \"Wild Bill\". Acaba de descubrir que su hermano se lo compró en "
"Italia y ahora se la tiene jurada a los alemanes."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/narrator/winters/04"
msgid "Let's go! We're moving out!"
msgstr "¡Vámonos! ¡Nos movemos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/obj_progress"
msgid "%1% out of 3 beacons deployed."
msgstr "%1% de 3 balizas desplegadas."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Excellent work! You have shown the enemy what you’re capable of. Thanks to "
"our radio beacons, the next wave of aircraft could locate the drop zones and "
"bring in the second wave. Great job!"
msgstr ""
"¡Buen trabajo! Habéis demostrado al enemigo de lo que sois capaces. Gracias "
"a nuestras radiobalizas, la siguiente oleada de aviones pudo localizar las "
"zonas de lanzamiento y traer la segunda oleada. "

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"You failed to complete the primary objective! Our troops won’t locate their "
"drop zones because the beacons were not deployed. The drops will be "
"scattered all over Normandy, and the Germans will maintain control over the "
"area. You must try again!"
msgstr ""
"No has podido completar el objetivo principal. Nuestras tropas no "
"localizarán sus zonas de lanzamiento porque las balizas no están "
"desplegadas. Los paracaidistas se dispersarán por toda Normandía y los "
"alemanes mantendrán el control de la zona ¡Inténtalo otra vez!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/place"
msgid "Pathfinders, 501st PIR, 101st \"Screaming Eagles\""
msgstr "Rastreadores, 501º PIR, 101º \"Screaming Eagles\""

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/scenario1"
msgid "Normandy, around the hamlet of Le Holdy, West of Ste-Marie-du-Mont."
msgstr ""
"Normandía, cerca de la aldea de Le Holdy, al oeste de Ste-Marie-du-Mont."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/scenario2"
msgid "Drop Zone \"Charlie\""
msgstr "Zona de aterrizaje \"Charlie\""

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/story"
msgid ""
"  On the evening of June 5th, 1944, a massive formation of C-47 aircraft "
"lifts off from RAF North Witham for Normandy. They will drop large numbers "
"of paratroopers behind the D-Day invasion beaches.\n"
"\n"
"  Thirty minutes ahead of them, the pathfinders of the 101st US airborne "
"division are already on their way! They are the first American troops to "
"land in German-occupied France. Several waves of para-drops and troop-"
"carrying gliders will bring in the airborne assault troops.\n"
"\n"
"  Less than one hour into D-Day, the Screaming Eagles’ 501st Parachute "
"Infantry Regiment jumps into action, with orders to place three small radio "
"beacons to guide the other aircraft in.\n"
"\n"
"Good luck!"
msgstr ""
"  En la tarde del 5 de junio de 1944, una gran formación de aviones C-47 "
"despega de la base de la RAF de North Witham con destino a Normandía. Su "
"objetivo es soltar un gran número de paracaidistas detrás de las líneas "
"enemigas, cerca playas de la invasión del Día D.\n"
"\n"
"  Treinta minutos antes que ellos, los rastreadores, conocidos como "
"\"Pathfinders\", de la 101ª división aerotransportada estadounidense están "
"ya en camino. Son las primeras tropas americanas que pisarán la Francia "
"ocupada. Varias oleadas de paracaidistas y planeadores llevarán después al "
"resto de tropas aerotransportadas.\n"
"\n"
"  A menos de una hora del Día D, el Regimiento de Infantería Paracaidista "
"501, \"Screaming Eagles\" entra en acción, con órdenes de colocar tres "
"pequeñas balizas para guiar a los demás aviones.\n"
"\n"
"¡Buena suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/task0"
msgid "Eliminate the German truck patrol."
msgstr "Elimina la patrulla de camiones alemana."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/task1"
msgid "Make contact with other paratroopers"
msgstr "Contacta con otros paracaidistas"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/task2"
msgid "Deploy the radio beacons in the designated locations."
msgstr "Despliegua las radiobalizas en los lugares designados."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/task3"
msgid ""
"Kill the German officer attempting to escape, preventing the arrival of "
"enemy reinforcements."
msgstr ""
"Mata al oficial alemán que intenta escapar, e impide así la llegada de "
"refuerzos del enemigo."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/task4"
msgid "Assault the farm and rescue the captured paratroopers. "
msgstr "Asalta la granja y rescata a los paracaidistas capturados. "

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/task5"
msgid "Take out the AA battery. "
msgstr "Elimina la batería antiaéreas."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/task6"
msgid "Eliminate the German reinforcements."
msgstr "Elimina los refuerzos alemanes."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/task_sec1"
msgid "Secret Objective #1"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/task_sec1_comp"
msgid ""
"(Secret Objective) Kill the collaborator before he raises the alarm and "
"brings German reinforcements."
msgstr ""
"(Objetivo secreto) Mata al colaborador antes de que dé la alarma y traiga "
"refuerzos alemanes."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_06_01_pathfinders/timestamp"
msgid "A few hours later..."
msgstr "Unas horas después..."
